snippet.title: Modulor - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
I've just announced my gun-building rogue-like.
⏩Wishlist now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2529710/Modulor/ 

Gather modules, build your gun and create crazy synergies to fight through randomly generated dungeons.
